% This function list for the R 'base' package is generated by running
%  ls *.Rd */*.Rd |sort |sed 's/.Rd$/} \\\\/g' |sed 's/^/{/g'
% in the folder
%  ${R-src}/src/library/base/man
%
% In general, this document can only be manually modified and should not
% be rebuilt from scratch, because many changes have been made since the
% initial list was created.

\newcommand\str[1]{\strut\hspace{.6\textwidth}#1}
  % string processing.
\newcommand\f[1]{\strut\hspace{.1\textwidth}#1}
  % manipulate functions.
\newcommand\obj[1]{\strut\hspace{.2\textwidth}#1}
  % manipulate atomic and generic objects.
\newcommand\lobj[1]{\strut\hspace{.3\textwidth}#1}
  % manipulate vectors, lists, matrices.
